## Project Structure

```
apps/
  api/           ← Bun + Hono API (runtime: bun {{.BunVersion}})
    src/
      index.ts   ← Entry point, graceful shutdown
      bootstrap.ts ← Module initialization (init order matters)
      config.ts  ← Env-based config, loaded once at startup
      router.ts  ← Hono router, middleware, routes
  web/           ← Vite + React frontend (TypeScript, Tailwind)
infra/
  docker-compose.yaml  ← Local dev infrastructure
Makefile         ← All common tasks
.env.example     ← Required environment variables
.modkit.yaml     ← Module registry manifest
```

